modName: Gray and White dog with green eyes etc
summary: Green eyes, gray paws and snout, pink pawpads, pink tongue, light black nose, etc.
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod! Just look at the screenshots to see what he looks like (I named him Bear on my game <3) I took about 10 minutes to do this lol it\'s not that great...Okay enjoy!

INSTALLING
      1. Take the folder and extract it to steam/steamapps/common/skyrim/data and then add the same file to skyrim textures/actors/dog folder...
